00:00:19.790 --> 00:00:21.850
 And we are given 2 equations. 

00:00:21.850 --> 00:00:26.500
 The first is blue, y = 7 / 5x - 5, 

00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:30.475
 and this is green, y = 3 / 5x - 1. 

00:00:30.475 --> 00:00:32.100
 Let's picture them graphically, 

00:00:32.100 --> 00:00:33.560
