00:00:33.560 --> 00:00:35.830
 First we depict y = 7 / 5x - 5. 

00:00:35.830 --> 00:00:39.820
 The first thing I notice is crossing the line in -5. 

00:00:39.820 --> 00:00:45.020
 In other words, when x = 0, y = -5. 

00:00:45.050 --> 00:00:46.320
 Let's check this out. 

00:00:46.320 --> 00:00:49.470
 If x = 0, then y = 7/5 * 0 - 5 

00:00:49.470 --> 00:00:51.230
 y = -5 

00:00:51.230 --> 00:00:53.160
 There is logic. 

00:00:53.160 --> 00:00:55.850
 And we see that the angular coefficient is 7/5. 

00:00:55.850 --> 00:00:59.320
